nd system deployers instill in agentic\nAI systems that could mitigate the possibility of errors and harms?", "metadata": {"producer": "LuaTeX-1.16.0", "creator": "LaTeX with hyperref", "creationdate": "2023-12-18T15:56:58+00:00", "source": "D:\\Users\\wpoga\\Documents\\Ebooks\\Artificial Intelligence\\practices-for-governing-agentic-ai-systems.pdf", "file_path": "D:\\Users\\wpoga\\Documents\\Ebooks\\Artificial Intelligence\\practices-for-governing-agentic-ai-systems.pdf", "total_pages": 23, "format": "PDF 1.5", "title": "", "author": "", "subject": "", "keywords": "", "moddate": "2023-12-18T15:56:58+00:00", "trapped": "", "modDate": "D:20231218155658Z", "creationDate": "D:20231218155658Z", "page": 10}, "type": "Document"}
